  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">After school programs to inspire children &amp; youth</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Clara Luna provides a space for the children and youth to engage in educational and creative activities, something very uncommon in Ecuador and especially in small towns like Puerto Lopez. With our after school programs, children are given an opportunity to do arts and crafts, read books, play games, and work together on community iniatives. They are taught skills like leadership, communication, and critical thinking, something severely lacking in the traditional school system</narrative>
  </description>
